{"tid":1431553,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"又有聲稱陳美齡既文章流出","createTime":"2019-08-08T04:26:33.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-08T05:15:01.000Z","uid":88133,"like":2,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"d030d36fc673b77b1447e9547f59d34d474d8ad4","tid":1431553,"uid":88133,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T04:26:33.000Z","msg":"又再流傳一篇聲稱由Agnes Chan  香港才女陳美齡寫既文，有無巴絲一齊inbox 陳美齡做FC<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n流傳既文章原文：<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n希望身邊朋友可以幫忙再分享<br />\n_________________________<br />\n<br />\nAgnes Chan  香港才女陳美齡<br />\n<br />\n*五無香港，還可撐幾耐？*<br />\n1）高官無能<br />\n2）政客無恥<br />\n3）學生無知<br />\n4）警員無奈<br />\n5）市民無辜<br />\n<br />\n現在天天遊行，日日衝擊，警方疲於奔命，警員也有洩氣之時，當出現無警狀態，香港會怎樣？<br />\n學生，示威者，盲目支持者氣燄日益高漲，高舉民主旗幟，就可為所欲為。<br />\n今後的香港沒有了和諧，進入了內戰，日日衝擊。示威者呼籲制裁中國，提高旅遊警示級別，呼籲外國遊客不要到香港。<br />\n美國，聯合國將香港，澳門剔除特別關稅區，真的制裁中國，香港，澳門。金融中心地位不保，外資撤走資金，金融市場崩潰，房地產樓價暴瀉。港元受到追擊，港資產貶值。對！樓價平到年青人可以置業，但工作沒有了，收入沒有了。樓價再平也徒然！<br />\n哀鴻遍野，全香港市民陪葬，失業，經濟倒退，負資產激增，通縮，旅遊業停頓，零售，飲食無法繼續經營，結業潮爆發，民不聊生。這樣的結局，是香港爭取民主所樂見嗎？請各位商界代表，教協代表，醫護代表，學生代表....。停一停，諗一諗。這樣爭取的所謂「民主」會長久嗎？「民主」帶來的負面影響，破壞了整個香港的生態。沒有了「生存」，民不聊生。得到的是「創傷性的民主」。一個雙輸的敗局。為何還要強行堅持爭取。政府已清楚民意，何不大家放下成見，將視線放在民生，造福香港市民。那不是更好的雙贏方法嗎？"},{"pid":"aa6ee532a4eeddab5da381d996b5a7a92c5723c7","tid":1431553,"uid":88133,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T04:27:04.000Z","msg":"自推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0b8561c5483d5cb0274508bc584b038dd8dfa0ff","tid":1431553,"uid":88133,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T04:27:14.000Z","msg":"自推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"67ab1b5c51edf6e267ac5d30d407e9ef34072426","tid":1431553,"uid":88133,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T04:27:34.000Z","msg":"自推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1e77cdbf42ddb3c5e10f1d7e335b3a0cb6e252d1","tid":1431553,"uid":88133,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T04:29:07.000Z","msg":"自推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f52856fc373d538547cdc882e59aae10816e5b1c","tid":1431553,"uid":88133,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T04:29:53.000Z","msg":"自推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a906d1cfccfb1abdf3547b982a26da0684e6105c","tid":1431553,"uid":88133,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T04:31:08.000Z","msg":"自推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5fc2220183f919e85dad9dfc3bd5b54f32d169ed","tid":1431553,"uid":122275,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T04:31:37.000Z","msg":"Who"},{"pid":"5a2118436cf8792f78553e16461aedf884d443dd","tid":1431553,"uid":88133,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T04:32:35.000Z","msg":"自推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><im