t;民主<br />\n本身已經窮無影響<br />\n呢下同你濫抄都無影響"},{"pid":"58a8f7cdf3d81d30e7031cfd2bae403099dd54c5","tid":1431553,"uid":75823,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T04:44:56.000Z","msg":"呢個日本婆係賤西一名"},{"pid":"347db0c1566e0bf2b01cbcd480e85d3d8b2eff53","tid":1431553,"uid":88133,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T04:55:43.000Z","msg":"幫手Inbox下佢，如果唔係佢寫又可以一大巴車落藍絲度<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d3638d90dda1ac765f899448708460d88a689c6f","tid":1431553,"uid":3241,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T04:56:39.000Z","msg":"唔係話曾經港共想搵佢做官？ <br />\n呢共狗黎嫁喎"},{"pid":"881c2de503a5f729c65d8329d32ddfedac5559c1","tid":1431553,"uid":179409,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T05:11:32.000Z","msg":"又將政治同民生分開嚟講<br />\n戇鳩之霸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e906e2a163b671534ff73b7e49d8c87d3e8715d9","tid":1431553,"uid":272976,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T05:12:10.000Z","msg":"救救劉細良<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1431682\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1431682</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"de9be5bdd72dc56256d16143298bbe0041388fdb","tid":1431553,"uid":52881,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T05:14:19.000Z","msg":"又係D各打五十大板嘅ON9文"},{"pid":"dd89436c3867dc373cfa194c2443fa65b341c2c1","tid":1431553,"uid":41374,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T05:15:01.000Z","msg":"黑警唔會無辜囉"}]}